---
import Default from "../layouts/Default.astro";
---

<Default title="Agent Ready — About">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 prose prose-zephyr">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zephyr-900 mb-2">About Agent Ready</h1>
    <p class="text-zephyr-700 mb-6">
      Agent Ready is a free, public, commerce-focused agent-readiness scanner. Paste a
      store URL — get a 0-100 score across 5 categories plus a fix-it action list.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zephyr-900 mt-8 mb-3">What we check</h2>
    <p class="text-zephyr-700">
      15 checks across discoverability, content, commerce protocols, product data,
      and checkout. The full matrix lives in
      <a
        class="underline"
        href="https://github.com/Weaverse/zephyr-scanner/blob/main/docs/CHECKS.md"
      >
        docs/CHECKS.md
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zephyr-900 mt-8 mb-3">Protocols covered</h2>
    <ul class="text-zephyr-700 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>UCP — Universal Commerce Protocol</li>
      <li>MCP — Model Context Protocol (server card discovery, SEP-2127)</li>
      <li>ACP — Agentic Commerce Protocol (Stripe + OpenAI)</li>
      <li>x402 — HTTP 402 payments (Coinbase)</li>
      <li>WebMCP — client-side tools for agents (W3C WebML CG)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zephyr-900 mt-8 mb-3">Who built this</h2>
    <p class="text-zephyr-700">
      Agent Ready is an open-source project from
      <a class="underline" href="https://weaverse.io">Weaverse</a>. We build
      Hydrogen apps and tooling for AI-first commerce.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zephyr-900 mt-8 mb-3">Scanner identity</h2>
    <p class="text-zephyr-700">
      Outbound requests carry
      <code class="font-mono text-sm">
        User-Agent: AgentReadyBot/0.1 (+https://isyourstoreagentready.com)
      </code>. Disallow this UA in your <code>robots.txt</code> to block scans.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zephyr-900 mt-8 mb-3">Contributing</h2>
    <p class="text-zephyr-700">
      MIT licensed. Contributions welcome — see
      <a
        class="underline"
        href="https://github.com/Weaverse/zephyr-scanner/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md"
      >
        CONTRIBUTING.md
      </a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Default>
